OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FPeople who visited a nightclub in Kent
OL,8,Fhave been urged to get antibiotics
OL,9,Famid a meningitis outbreak in which
OL,10,Ftwo students have died.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fis advising anyone who visited Club
OL,14,FChemistry in Canterbury on March 5, 6
OL,15,For 7 to come forward for preventative
OL,16,Fantibiotic treatment as a
OL,17,F"precautionary measure".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
