OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe government agency said on Monday
OL,8,Fevening that it was continuing to
OL,9,Finvestigate the outbreak of
OL,10,Fmeningitis, with 13 cases notified
OL,11,Fsince March 13, including two deaths.
OL,13,FA Year 13 pupil in Faversham and a
OL,14,Fstudent at the University of Kent have
OL,15,Fdied in the outbreak, with others
OL,16,Fbeing treated in hospital.
OL,18,FTwo sites in Kent were open for the
OL,19,Fpublic to collect antibiotics on
OL,20,FMonday, and a further two are planned
OL,21,Fto open on Tuesday morning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FLouise Jones-Roberts, the owner of
OL,8,FClub Chemistry, said more than 2,000
OL,9,Fpeople would have visited the venue
OL,10,Fover the three dates.
OL,12,FThose who visited now need tracing for
OL,13,Fantibiotics.
OL,15,FMs Jones-Roberts said she had been
OL,16,Ftold that one confirmed case of
OL,17,Fmeningitis had been linked to the club
OL,18,Flast weekend, but the dates had now
OL,19,Fbeen confirmed as being linked to the
OL,20,Fweekend of March 5 to 7.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FShe said: "I've been told they started
OL,8,Fshowing symptoms on March 10."
OL,10,FMs Jones-Roberts added: "I wouldn't
OL,11,Fhave opened this weekend if I'd known
OL,12,Fbut I didn't know.
OL,14,F"I'm worried about another potential
OL,15,Foutbreak from this weekend."
OL,17,FShe said she had managed to contact
OL,18,Faround 90 out of 95 members of staff
OL,19,Fat the club and they had gone to get
OL,20,Fantibiotics.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@^O]rD@YOUvD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FMs Jones-Roberts added: "I'm
OL,8,Fdevastated for the families affected.
OL,9,FIt's so incredibly sad.
OL,11,F"I just really hope people know the
OL,12,Fsymptoms and no more lives are lost."
OL,14,FShe said the club would remain closed
OL,15,Funtil further notice, adding: "It is
OL,16,Fnot a hard decision to close ` we are
OL,17,Ftalking about people's lives."
OL,19,FMs Jones-Roberts told the BBC that a
OL,20,Fmember of staff at the nightclub is
OL,21,Fone of the confirmed cases.
OL,26,@oD@YOUsD@AOUtD@eO]wD@_OUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
