PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FShe said: "He is in hospital, he is
OL,8,Fbeing treated, and he's awaiting
OL,9,Ffurther tests to see if the treatment
OL,10,Fhe's had has improved his condition.
OL,12,F"We've got two other members of staff
OL,13,Fwho are currently in A&E with
OL,14,Fsuspected meningitis, and we're just
OL,15,Fwaiting for the update from them for
OL,16,Ftheir test results."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
