PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FTrish Mannes, UKHSA regional deputy
OL,8,Fdirector for the South East, said:
OL,9,F"Our investigations have identified
OL,10,Fthat some cases visited Club Chemistry
OL,11,Fin Canterbury and it is important that
OL,12,Fanyone who visited the club between
OL,13,FMarch 5 and March 7 now comes forward
OL,14,Ffor preventative antibiotic treatment
OL,15,Fas a precaution, as well as those
OL,16,Foffered antibiotics at the university
OL,17,F` these students are being contacted
OL,18,Fdirectly through the university."
OL,26,@qD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
