OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe UKHSA has issued advice to 16,000
OL,8,Fstaff and students at the University
OL,9,Fof Kent, where antibiotics are also
OL,10,Fbeing offered to those who need them.
OL,12,FAt the campus on Monday, students,
OL,13,Fsome of which were wearing face masks,
OL,14,Fdescribed their worries as they queued
OL,15,Ffor antibiotics.
OL,17,FThe UKHSA said it acted as soon as it
OL,18,Fwas notified of a cluster of cases.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
