OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FAmelia McIlroy, the headteacher of
OL,8,FQueen Elizabeth's Grammar School in
OL,9,FFaversham, confirmed one of its Year
OL,10,F13 pupils had died.
OL,12,FShe said: "It is with great sadness
OL,13,Fthat we are confirming the loss of
OL,14,FJuliette, a much-loved and treasured
OL,15,Fmember of our school community.
OL,17,F"Juliette was a student at our school
OL,18,Ffor seven years.
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"She was incredibly kind, thoughtful
OL,8,Fand intelligent and she loved our
OL,9,Fschool and was very happy here.
OL,11,F"Juliette embraced everything that
OL,12,Fschool had to offer with great
OL,13,Fenthusiasm and joy and her humour and
OL,14,Fpositivity were captivating.
OL,16,F"She was a genuinely caring and
OL,17,Fattentive listener, a true friend `
OL,18,Fwho listened with warmth, respect and
OL,19,Fsincere interest to her peers and to
OL,20,Four staff.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,F"In short, she was a lovely girl ` her
OL,8,Fbeautiful smile, her loving nature and
OL,9,Fher sense of fun will be hugely missed.
OL,11,F"We are all devastated.
OL,13,F"Our love and thoughts are with her
OL,14,Ffamily and friends at this terribly
OL,15,Fsad time."
OL,17,FJuliette's father told the BBC that
OL,18,Fthe family are "beyond devastated and
OL,19,Fthey have no words to express their
OL,20,Floss".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@AOUwD@JO]zD@POU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
