PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FThe headmaster of Simon Langton
OL,8,FGrammar School for Boys said in a
OL,9,Fletter to parents that one of its Year
OL,10,F13 students has been admitted to
OL,11,Fhospital with meningitis.
OL,13,FAn update sent to parents at Norton
OL,14,FKnatchbull School in Ashford, Kent,
OL,15,Fconfirmed a diagnosis for a Year 13
OL,16,Fstudent admitted to hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FRosie Duffield, Independent MP for
OL,8,FCanterbury, said she has received a
OL,9,Fbriefing from the UKHSA, which is
OL,10,Fstressing that meningitis needs
OL,11,F"fairly intimate contact" to spread
OL,12,Fbetween people.
OL,14,FShe said people could contact her
OL,15,Foffice if they were worried.
OL,17,FA University of Kent spokesperson said
OL,18,Fon Monday it was taking advice from
OL,19,Fthe UKHSA and communicating with
OL,20,Fstudents and staff.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
