PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773765957
OL,3,CPeople who visited nightclub urged to
OL,4,Cget antibiotics amid meningitis
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FIt said that there will be no in-
OL,8,Fperson assessments or exams for
OL,9,Fstudents this week.
OL,11,FPeople who attended Club Chemistry can
OL,12,Fcollect antibiotics from: the Gate
OL,13,FClinic at Kent and Canterbury
OL,14,FHospital; Westgate Hall on Westgate
OL,15,FHall Road, Canterbury; the Carey
OL,16,FBuilding, Thanet Hub, Margate
OL,17,FNorthwood Road; and the Senate
OL,18,Fbuilding at the University of Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
